{"word":"G2854 - κολλούριον - kolloúrion - kol-loo'-ree-on - Eyesalve","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κολλούριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kolloúrion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kol-loo'-ree-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Eyesalve</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"கலிக்கம் - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"eye salve, a poultice"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a presumed derivative of <b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;</b> <b>kollura</b> (a <i>cake</i>; probably akin to the base of <a href=\"#/G2853 - κολλάω - kolláō - kol-lah'-o/2853\">G2853</a>); properly a <i>poultice</i> (as made of or in the form of <i>crackers</i>), that is, (by analogy) a <i>plaster:</i> - eyesalve.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}